  "english": [
    "<strong>GEMARA:</strong> <b>Whose</b> opinion is expressed in <b>the mishna? It is</b> apparently the opinion of <b>Rabbi Meir. As, if</b> it is the opinion of <b>Rabbi Yehuda,</b> there is a contradiction, because <b>he does not differentiate</b> whether one takes a vow by saying: <b>An offering, and he does not differentiate</b> whether he takes a vow by saying: <b>This offering.</b> In both cases the vow does not take effect, as he did not use the phrase: Like an offering. The mishna, by contrast, indicates that only a vow that is phrased: An offering that I will not eat of yours, or: This offering that I will eat of yours, does not take effect. If it is phrased: An offering I will eat of yours, it takes effect, as it indicates that his eating will be like an offering.",
    "The Gemara continues its analysis: <b>Say the latter clause</b> of the mishna: If he says: That which <b>I will not eat of yours</b> is <b>not an offering,</b> the food is <b>permitted.</b> The Gemara asks: <b>But didn’t we learn</b> in a mishna (13a) that if one said: That which <b>I will not eat of yours</b> will be <b>for an offering [<i>lekorban</i>], Rabbi Meir forbids</b> the food to him? <b>And Rabbi Abba said</b> that <b>it is rendered as one who says:</b> Your food <b>will be</b> to me <b>for an offering; therefore, I will not eat of yours.</b> The mishna appears to be incompatible with the opinion of Rabbi Meir as well.",
    "The Gemara answers that this is <b>not difficult. That</b> mishna is referring to one <b>who said: For an offering [<i>lekorban</i>],</b> and the vow therefore takes effect. <b>This</b> mishna is referring to one <b>who said: Not for an offering [<i>la lekorban</i>],</b> where <b>he is saying that it should not be an offering,</b> and therefore the vow does not take effect.",
    "<strong>MISHNA:</strong> If one says: <b>An oath</b> that <b>I will not eat of yours,</b> or: <b>This</b> is <b>an oath that I will eat of yours [<i>she’okhal lekha</i>],</b> or: <b>Not an oath that I will not eat of yours,</b> the food <b>is forbidden.</b>",
    "<strong>GEMARA:</strong> <b>By inference</b> from the mishna, it may be derived <b>that</b> the statement: <b>This is an oath that I will eat of yours, indicates that I will not eat. And</b> the Gemara <b>raises a contradiction</b> from a mishna (<i>Shevuot</i> 19b): There are <b>two</b> basic types of <b>oaths that are</b> in fact <b>four:</b> An oath <b>that I will eat, and: That I will not eat;</b> an oath <b>that I ate, and: That I did not eat. From</b> the fact <b>that</b> the mishna <b>states:</b> That I will eat, in contradistinction to: <b>That I will not eat; that I ate, and</b> in contradistinction: <b>That I did not eat,</b> it may be derived <b>by inference that</b> an oath <b>that I will eat of yours [<i>she’okhal lekha</i>] indicates:</b> An oath <b>that I will eat.</b> This contradicts our mishna.",
    "<b>Abaye said:</b> The phrase: <b>That I will eat [<i>she’okhal</i>], indicates two expressions,</b> depending on the context in which it is used. How so? If <b>they were importuning [<i>mesarevin</i>] him to eat, and he said: I will eat, I will eat, and</b> he <b>furthermore</b> said: <b>An oath that I will eat [<i>she’okhal</i>], it indicates: That I will eat. However,</b> if <b>he said: I will not eat, I will not eat, and he furthermore said: An oath that I will eat [<i>she’okhal</i>], he is saying: That I will not eat.</b> The oath is intended to reinforce his refusal to eat.",
    "<b>Rav Ashi said</b> that the phrase: <b>That I will eat [<i>she’okhal</i>],</b> cited in the mishna <b>with regard to an oath, is</b> actually <b>saying</b> that <b>he said: That I will not eat [<i>she’i okhal</i>].</b> The Gemara asks: <b>If so,</b> the prohibition <b>is obvious,</b> as he explicitly took an oath not to eat. <b>What</b> is the purpose <b>of stating</b> this <i>halakha</i>? The Gemara answers: <b>Lest you say</b> that <b>he blundered</b> in properly <b>upholding the wording,</b> i.e., he mispronounced the vow, as his intention was to say: An oath that I will eat [<i>she’okhal</i>], the mishna <b>teaches us</b> that he meant that he will not eat.",
    "<b>Abaye did not state</b> the <b>reason</b> for the ruling of the mishna that was stated <b>by Rav Ashi, as</b> the mishna <b>does not teach</b> the case of: <b>That I will not eat [<i>she’i okhal</i>].</b> Rather, it teaches the case of that I will eat [<i>she’okhal</i>].",
    "<b>And Rav Ashi turned away [<i>nadei</i>] from the reason that Abaye</b> stated, because <b>he held</b> that the phrase: <b>That I will not eat, also indicates two expressions,</b> depending on the context. For example, if <b>they were importuning him to eat and he said: I will not eat, I will not eat, and</b> subsequently <b>he</b> also <b>said: An oath,</b> then, in this case, <b>whether</b> the wording of the oath was: <b>That I will eat, or: That I will not eat, this</b> expression <b>indicates that he is saying: I will eat.</b> The statement: An oath that I will not eat, should be interpreted rhetorically in this context: Did I take an oath that I will not eat? Certainly I did not, as I will eat.",
    "<b>And there is also</b> a way <b>to interpret the expression: An oath that I will not eat,</b> as <b>indicating</b> its straightforward meaning, i.e., that he is <b>saying: An oath that I will not eat.</b> Therefore, the mishna cannot be interpreted in this manner. <b>Rather, the <i>tanna</i></b> in tractate <i>Shevuot</i> clearly <b>established a principle: That I will eat, indicates that I will eat, and: That I will not eat, indicates I will not eat.</b> Therefore, the correct version of the mishna must be: That I will not eat [<i>she’i okhal</i>].",
    "<strong>MISHNA:</strong> <b>This</b> rule, that oaths can render actions, which do not have actual substance, either prohibited or obligatory, <b>is a stringency of oaths vis-à-vis vows,</b> which do not take effect with regard to matters that do not have actual substance. <b>And</b> there is also <b>a stringency of vows vis-à-vis oaths. How so?</b> With regard to one who <b>said: Making a <i>sukka</i> is <i>konam</i> for me,</b> or: <b>Taking a <i>lulav</i> is</b> <i>konam</i> <b>for me,</b> or: <b>Donning phylacteries is</b> <i>konam</i> <b>for me, in</b> the case of <b>vows,</b> the items are rendered <b>forbidden,</b> and he may not perform the mitzva until the vow is dissolved. However, <b>in</b> the case of similar <b>oaths,</b> these items are <b>permitted, as one cannot take an oath to transgress the mitzvot.</b>"
  ],
  "gemara": [
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sentence\" id=\"0\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><big><strong>גְּמָ׳</strong></big> מַנִּי מַתְנִיתִין — <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Meir, fifth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"2068\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Meir\" data-name-he=\"רבי מאיר\">רַבִּי מֵאִיר</span> הִיא, דְּאִי <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Yehuda bar Rabbi Elai, fifth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"1395\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Yehuda bar Rabbi Elai\" data-name-he=\"רבי יהודה ברבי אילעאי\">רַבִּי יְהוּדָה</span> —",
      "segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "לָא שָׁנֵי לֵיהּ ״קׇרְבָּן״ וְלָא שָׁנֵי לֵיהּ ״הַקׇּרְבָּן״. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"1\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>אֵימָא",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "סֵיפָא: ״לַקׇּרְבָּן לֹא אוֹכַל לָךְ״ — מוּתָּר. וְהָתְנַן:",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "״לַקׇּרְבָּן לֹא אוֹכַל לָךְ״ — <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Meir, fifth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"2068\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Meir\" data-name-he=\"רבי מאיר\">רַבִּי מֵאִיר</span> אוֹסֵר, וְאָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabbi Akiva I, second-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"6\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Akiva I\" data-name-he=\"רבי אבא\" data-crossline-group=\"name-ref-crossline-52599\">רַבִּי</span>",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabbi Akiva I, second-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"6\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Akiva I\" data-name-he=\"רבי אבא\" data-crossline-group=\"name-ref-crossline-52599\">אַבָּא</span>: נַעֲשָׂה כְּאוֹמֵר: ״לַקׇּרְבָּן יְהֵא, לְפִיכָךְ לֹא",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אוֹכַל לָךְ״. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"2\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>לָא קַשְׁיָא: הָא דְּאָמַר ״לַקׇּרְבָּן״, הָא",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "דְּאָמַר ״לָא לְקׇרְבָּן״ — דְּלָא הָוֵי קׇרְבָּן קָאָמַר<span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-vilna-piska\" data-sugya-kind=\"vilna-piska\" data-sugya-id=\"34\" data-raw-symbol=\"׃\">׃</span>",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-steinsaltz\" data-sugya-kind=\"steinsaltz\" data-sugya-id=\"42\" data-sentence-id=\"3\" data-steinsaltz-label=\"ב משנה\">§</span> <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"3\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><a class=\"piska-quote-link\" data-piska-quote-group=\"piska-quote-35\" href=\"/nedarim/16a#gemara-line-8\" title=\"Mishnah source: Nedarim 16a\"><big><strong>מַתְנִי׳</strong></big> שְׁבוּעָה לֹא אוֹכַל לָךְ, הָא שְׁבוּעָה</a>",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<a class=\"piska-quote-link\" data-piska-quote-group=\"piska-quote-35\" href=\"/nedarim/16a#gemara-line-8\" title=\"Mishnah source: Nedarim 16a\">שֶׁאוֹכַל לָךְ, לָא שְׁבוּעָה לֹא אוֹכַל לָךְ — אָסוּר</a><span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-vilna-piska\" data-sugya-kind=\"vilna-piska\" data-sugya-id=\"35\" data-raw-symbol=\"׃\">׃</span>",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-steinsaltz\" data-sugya-kind=\"steinsaltz\" data-sugya-id=\"43\" data-sentence-id=\"4\" data-steinsaltz-label=\"ג גמרא\">§</span> <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"4\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><big><strong>גְּמָ׳</strong></big> מִכְּלָל דְּהָא שְׁבוּעָה שֶׁאוֹכַל לָךְ — דְּלָא",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אָכֵילְנָא מַשְׁמַע. וּרְמִינְהוּ: שְׁבוּעוֹת שְׁתַּיִם",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "שֶׁהֵן אַרְבַּע. שֶׁאוֹכַל וְשֶׁלֹּא אוֹכַל, שֶׁאָכַלְתִּי",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "וְשֶׁלֹּא אָכַלְתִּי. מִדְּקָאָמַר שֶׁלֹּא אוֹכַל,",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "שֶׁאָכַלְתִּי וְשֶׁלֹּא אָכַלְתִּי, מִכְּלָל דְּשֶׁאוֹכַל לָךְ —",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "דְּאָכֵילְנָא מַשְׁמַע! <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"5\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Abaye, fourth-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"121\" data-full-name=\"Abaye\" data-name-he=\"אביי\">אַבָּיֵי</span>: ״שֶׁאוֹכַל״ שְׁתֵּי",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "לְשׁוֹנוֹת מַשְׁמַע. הָיוּ מְסָרְבִין בּוֹ לֶאֱכוֹל, וְאָמַר:",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "״אָכֵילְנָא אָכֵילְנָא״, וְתוּ: ״שְׁבוּעָה שֶׁאוֹכַל״ — דְּאָכֵילְנָא",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מַשְׁמַע. אֲבָל אָמַר: ״לָא אָכֵילְנָא לָא אָכֵילְנָא״,",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "וְתוּ אָמַר: ״שְׁבוּעָה שֶׁאוֹכַל״ — ״דְּלָא אָכֵילְנָא״ קָאָמַר.",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sentence\" id=\"6\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Ashi, sixth-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"571\" data-full-name=\"Rav Ashi\" data-name-he=\"רב אשי\">רַב אָשֵׁי</span> אָמַר: ״שֶׁאוֹכַל״ דִּשְׁבוּעָה — ״שֶׁאִי אוֹכַל״",
      "segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "קָאָמַר. אִם כֵּן, פְּשִׁיטָא! מַאי לְמֵימְרָא? מַהוּ דְּתֵימָא:",
      "segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מֵיקַם לִישָּׁנָא הִיא דְּאִיתְּקִיל לֵיהּ, קָא מַשְׁמַע לַן. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"7\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Abaye, fourth-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"121\" data-full-name=\"Abaye\" data-name-he=\"אביי\">אַבָּיֵי</span>",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "לָא אָמַר טַעַם <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Ashi, sixth-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"571\" data-full-name=\"Rav Ashi\" data-name-he=\"רב אשי\">כְּרַב אָשֵׁי</span> — דְּלָא קָתָנֵי ״שֶׁאִי",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אוֹכַל״. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"8\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Ashi, sixth-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"571\" data-full-name=\"Rav Ashi\" data-name-he=\"רב אשי\">וְרַב אָשֵׁי</span> נָאדֵי מִן טַעַם <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Abaye, fourth-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"121\" data-full-name=\"Abaye\" data-name-he=\"אביי\">דְּאַבָּיֵי</span>. קָסָבַר",
      "segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "״שֶׁלֹּא אוֹכַל״ נָמֵי, מַשְׁמַע שְׁתֵּי לְשׁוֹנוֹת. הָיוּ",
      "segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מְסָרְבִין בּוֹ לֶאֱכוֹל וְאָמַר: ״לָא אָכֵילְנָא לָא",
      "segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אָכֵילְנָא״, וְאָמַר נָמֵי: ״שְׁבוּעָה״, בֵּין ״שֶׁאוֹכַל״",
      "segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "בֵּין ״שֶׁלֹּא אוֹכַל״ — הָדֵין ״אָכֵילְנָא״ מַשְׁמַע",
      "segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "דְּאָמַר. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"9\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>וְאִיכָּא לְתָרוֹצַהּ נָמֵי לִישָּׁנָא ״שְׁבוּעָה",
      "segment_ids": [
        9
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "שֶׁלֹּא אוֹכַל״ — ״שְׁבוּעָה דְּלָא אָכֵילְנָא״ קָאָמַר.",
      "segment_ids": [
        9
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אֶלָּא תַּנָּא פַּסְקַהּ: ״שֶׁאוֹכַל״ — ״דְּאָכֵילְנָא״",
      "segment_ids": [
        9
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מַשְׁמַע, וְ״שֶׁלֹּא אוֹכַל״ — ״לֹא אוֹכַל״ מַשְׁמַע<span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-vilna-piska\" data-sugya-kind=\"vilna-piska\" data-sugya-id=\"36\" data-raw-symbol=\"׃\">׃</span>",
      "segment_ids": [
        9
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-steinsaltz\" data-sugya-kind=\"steinsaltz\" data-sugya-id=\"44\" data-sentence-id=\"10\" data-steinsaltz-label=\"ד משנה\">§</span> <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"10\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><a class=\"piska-quote-link\" data-piska-quote-group=\"piska-quote-37\" href=\"/nedarim/16a#gemara-line-33\" title=\"Mishnah source: Nedarim 16a\"><big><strong>מַתְנִי׳</strong></big> זֶה חוֹמֶר בַּשְּׁבוּעוֹת מִבַּנְּדָרִים, וְחוֹמֶר</a>",
      "segment_ids": [
        10
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<a class=\"piska-quote-link\" data-piska-quote-group=\"piska-quote-37\" href=\"/nedarim/16a#gemara-line-33\" title=\"Mishnah source: Nedarim 16a\">בַּנְּדָרִים מִבַּשְּׁבוּעוֹת. כֵּיצַד? אָמַר: ״קֻוֽנָּם</a>",
      "segment_ids": [
        10
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<a class=\"piska-quote-link\" data-piska-quote-group=\"piska-quote-37\" href=\"/nedarim/16a#gemara-line-33\" title=\"Mishnah source: Nedarim 16a\">סוּכָּה שֶׁאֲנִי עוֹשֶׂה״, ״לוּלָב שֶׁאֲנִי נוֹטֵל״, ״תְּפִילִּין</a>",
      "segment_ids": [
        10
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<a class=\"piska-quote-link\" data-piska-quote-group=\"piska-quote-37\" href=\"/nedarim/16a#gemara-line-33\" title=\"Mishnah source: Nedarim 16a\">שֶׁאֲנִי מַנִּיחַ״ — בַּנְּדָרִים אָסוּר, בַּשְּׁבוּעוֹת</a>",
      "segment_ids": [
        10
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<a class=\"piska-quote-link\" data-piska-quote-group=\"piska-quote-37\" href=\"/nedarim/16a#gemara-line-33\" title=\"Mishnah source: Nedarim 16a\">מוּתָּר, שֶׁאֵין נִשְׁבָּעִין לַעֲבוֹר עַל הַמִּצְוֹת</a><span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-vilna-piska\" data-sugya-kind=\"vilna-piska\" data-sugya-id=\"37\" data-raw-symbol=\"׃\">׃</span>",
      "segment_ids": [
        10
      ]
    }
  ],
  "rashi": [
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>גְּמָ׳ מַתְנִיתִין</b> דהכא לא קתני דלהוי מותר אלא הקרבן שאוכל",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ולא קרבן שאוכל ואהכי רבי מאיר היא ולא רבי יהודה: <b>אֵימָא סֵיפָא</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>״לַקׇּרְבָּן לֹא אוֹכַל לָךְ״ מוּתָּר. <span class=\"dh-divergent\">והא</span> <span class=\"dh-divergent\">תנן</span></b> באידך פירקין לקרבן לא אוכל",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לך וכו': <b>הָא דְּאָמַר ״לַקׇּרְבָּן״.</b> אסור ומתניתין דקתני מותר דאמר לא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לקרבן דמשמע לא להוי קרבן מה שלא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "אוכל לך דאם אוכל ליהוי קרבן",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דהיינו מכלל לאו הן ולית ליה לרבי",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מאיר מכלל לאו הן: <b>מַתְנִי׳ שְׁבוּעָה</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>לֹא אוֹכַל לָךְ, <span class=\"dh-divergent\">כו&#x27;</span> הָא שְׁבוּעָה שֶׁאוֹכַל</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>אָסוּר.</b> כדמפרש בגמרא דהאי שאוכל",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לא אוכל משמע כלומר שבועה תהא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "חלה עלי אם אוכל והאי שבועה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ליכא למימר דחיי שבועה קאמר",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דשבועה לית בה ממש כמו בקרבן",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "אלא שבועה ממש קאמר: <b>לָא שְׁבוּעָה</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>לֹא אוֹכַל לָךְ אָסוּר.</b> אפי' לרבי מאיר",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דהכי גמרינן במסכת שבועות (<a href=\"/shevuot/36a\">דף לו.</a>)",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דבשבועה אית ליה לר\"מ מכלל לאו",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "אתה שומע הן: <b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">גמ&#x27;</span> ״שֶׁאוֹכַל״ שְׁתֵּי</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:6:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>לְשׁוֹנוֹת מַשְׁמַע. הָיוּ מְסָרְבִין.</b> מפצירים",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:6:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שיאכל ואמר אכילנא אכילנא ומתוך",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:6:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "כך אמר שבועה שאוכל משמע",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:6:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דאכילנא קאמר: (כשלא היו מסרבין",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:6:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בו אלא מעצמו אמר שבועה שאוכל):",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:6:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>רַב אָשֵׁי <span class=\"dh-divergent\">אומר</span>.</b> הא דקתני הא שבועה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:7:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שאוכל שאי אוכל קתני ולהכי אסור",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:7:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דלא אכילנא הוא: <b>פְּשִׁיטָא.</b> דודאי אי",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:7:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "קאמר שאי אוכל ודאי לא אכילנא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:7:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "הוא ואסור: <b>מַהוּ דְּתֵימָא.</b> האי דקאמר",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:7:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שאי אוכל מיקם לישנא כלומר תקון",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:7:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "הלשון הוא דבדעתו היה לומר",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:7:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שאוכל ונתקל ואמר שאי אוכל ונימא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:7:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לעולם להוי כמאן דאמר שאוכל קא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:7:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "משמע לן דלא דודאי אסור: <b>אַבָּיֵי</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:8:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>לָא אָמַר <span class=\"dh-divergent\">כטעמא</span> <span class=\"dh-divergent\">דרב</span> אָשֵׁי דְּלָא</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:8:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>קָתָנֵי</b> במתני' שאי אוכל: <b>ורב</b> <b>אשי</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:8:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>הוה</b> <b>נאדי.</b> נדוד וסור מטעמיה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:8:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דאביי דכי היו מסרבין בו לאכול ואמר",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:8:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לא אכילנא לא אכילנא ותו אמר",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:8:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שבועה בין אם אמר שבועה שאוכל",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:8:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בין אם אמר שבועה שלא אוכל",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:8:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "משמע דקאמר אכילנא אם אמר",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:8:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שבועה שאוכל משמע קאמר אכילנא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:8:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דהכי קאמר בתמיה לא אכילנא לא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:8:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "אכילנא שבועה שאוכל בודאי ואם",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:8:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "אמר שבועה שלא אוכל הדין משמע",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:8:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "נמי דאכילנא דמשמע לא אכילנא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:8:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שבועה אי לא אכילנא והיינו חדא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:8:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לישנא: <b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">והא</span> <span class=\"dh-divergent\">איכא</span> <span class=\"dh-divergent\">נמי</span> <span class=\"dh-divergent\">לתרוצי</span>.</b> בניחותא דמשמע לישנא אחרינא והאי",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:10:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דאמר שבועה שלא אוכל דלא אכילנא משמע דהאי דאמר לא אכילנא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:10:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בניחותא קאמר אם כן לא להוי אסור אי נמי כי אמר במתניתין שבועה לא אוכל אלא ודאי ליתא לטעמא דאביי אלא ודאי תנא במסכת",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:10:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שבועות דשאוכל דאכילנא משמע ולא ענין אחר ושלא אוכל משמע דלא אכילנא ולא דבר אחר הלכך מתרץ מתניתין שאי אוכל דכשאוכל ודאי",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:10:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לאו משמע אלא אי אמר דאכילנא: <b>מַתְנִי׳ זֶה חוֹמֶר בַּשְּׁבוּעוֹת מִבַּנְּדָרִים.</b> הא דאמרן שבועה שלא אוכל כו' דבשבועות אסור ובנדרים מותר:",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16a:11:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        9
      ]
    }
  ],
  "vilna_piskaot": [
    {
      "id": 34,
